SermonAudio,com,is,a,library,of,free,MP,audio,sermons,from,churches,and,ministries,all,over,the,world,Users,can,search,by,topics,Bibles,speakers,and,more,The,SermonAudio,com,API,allows,developers,to,access,and,interact,with,data,on,the,site,using,any,client,front,end,and,on,any,platform,Some,of,the,API,s,functions,include,listing,favorite,sermons,searching,for,sermons,by,keyword,and,adding,sermons